{"tid":2283260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"減脂一問","createTime":"2020-11-12T12:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T01:57:12.000Z","uid":40145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6d1ac5ba5c876b9e004b7c8ce0e3fd27f9d7b6","tid":2283260,"uid":40145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"最近幾個月小弟愛上左健身，咁就認真做左4,5個月到，由體脂25%減到宜家目測18%到。本身諗住減到15%到or減埋lower abs個少少脂肪就會開始bulk大隻d，問題係宜家冇access去任何gym (lockdown)，最少仲有3個禮拜先可以去翻gym。 咁我聽人講話如果你個training volume降低左 (好似我宜家係home workout)，本身已經會有potential muscle loss，再加上我宜家因為減脂caloric deficit緊，就會再lose多d muscle，咁我係咪應該食翻maintenance 維持住唔好比佢有咁多muscle loss，等有得去翻gym先再繼續減？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618a89208fadd10d59da390bc99ab6837c7a4baf","tid":2283260,"uid":40145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32605973a728bc23d16d590089c2f547ccbbb32b","tid":2283260,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bd4f39c0dbb21ead4873eb7e464d06534fe1684","tid":2283260,"uid":376967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"如果屋企有dumbbell盡量都要keep做，因為停gym太耐肌肉一定會流失"},{"pid":"f8de239c814b4394ae4e01eb4216748a6bb51e0f","tid":2283260,"uid":376967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bd4f39c0dbb21ead4873eb7e464d06534fe1684","tid":2283260,"uid":376967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"如果屋企有dumbbell盡量都要keep做，因為停gym太耐肌肉一定會流失"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:29:01.000Z","msg":"Protein一定唔可以少，每日都要食番足個量"},{"pid":"ddabe8c4021da283cfc1d509d5d8f78434931529","tid":2283260,"uid":40145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32605973a728bc23d16d590089c2f547ccbbb32b","tid":2283260,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"